{"tid":310112,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人冇諗過要拍拖","createTime":"2017-07-05T14:17:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-25T14:07:38.000Z","uid":7699,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5a35088080e9704591ab639cf1eedb8638462acd","tid":310112,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T14:17:19.000Z","msg":"利申先：自己本身都多女仔fd 但對任何一個女仔fd都冇非分之想<br />\n<br />\n見到一個個fd出pool 老老實實 羨慕點都有d 但有時聽到佢地呻對方有咩唔好 見到佢地點鬧交 反而令自己更加唔想出pool<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋我自認係一個幾自我中心嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔太想將時間心機金錢擺喺另一個人度（屋企人除外）同埋我覺得依家用自己時間金錢做自己鍾意做嘅野 自己一條友去下旅行咁仲開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有時諗 咁樣過一世人 無拘無束仲開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2944b3b97afac1b4fb8ab6a2f3423ed555e43783","tid":310112,"uid":7699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T14:21:16.000Z","msg":"同埋自己都幾討厭小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 更加冇結婚嘅需要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39689a37548df7a02542c39a2dbe7d4809a2c843","tid":310112,"uid":57990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T14:21:39.000Z","msg":"開心咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"081a461793dfee742860c04367305e9012d1e0ba","tid":310112,"uid":52942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T14:28:43.000Z","msg":"有時我覺得1+1=0.5 既機會大過1+1=2太多，計返個expected value 不如自己一個，生活已經夠辛苦，唔想增加負擔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0e3f6b0ce44d370b60b8ebb98c92439f51e2a1b","tid":310112,"uid":73935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T14:29:08.000Z","msg":"寂寞的人才渴望拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f873aa32ff729663b4d62d26b77a604c5f8e118c","tid":310112,"uid":7699,"like":0,"di